h3. Issue Summary

API responses suddenly missing email Address field in response body only for few users.
h3. Steps to Reproduce
 # [https://sitename.atlassian.net/rest/api/3/user?accountId=]<accountID>

h3. Expected Results
{code:java}
"self": "https://priyacs.atlassian.net/rest/api/3/user?accountId=5e5640343011ed0c8f8b",
    "accountId": "5e5640343011ed0c8f8b",
